text: Conrad Rochat (10 July 1927 - 24 May 2014) was a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
